Chelsea defender Branislav Ivanovic said: ‘We have the great result from Paris but we still have to think about the Champions League because we want to go through.

‘For us as a team it’s very good because we can have time to refresh ourselves and at the same time to work and prepare for the game in every detail. For sure, we will be ready for the game.

‘This is very important and a good thing about this is we can focus 100 per cent on Paris and we are not thinking about anything else.

‘We enjoyed and celebrated the win for the trophy because we deserved that, but we switched off the next morning and we now have the time to recover and think.

